Found a pizza oven on eBay listed by this company (on a Friday evening). eBay put limits on my account as did PayPal because I don’t use either very often. I couldn’t get anything lifted due to call centers being closed from Covid. Also couldn’t get ahold of my bank until Monday. The guys worked me every step of the way, took the oven off their website and eBay so I didn’t sell while I was waiting on banks.  Monday morning I was able to pay and they had already started preparing it for shipping. Not a smooth transaction by any means (100% on my end) but they were very gracious and understanding of the circumstances. When the time comes, I’ll definitely do business with them again. Thanks!
